videos.description: Alanna Smith scores 18 points and Karlie Samuelson adds 14 of her own to rally No. 10 Stanford past  No. 6 Oregon State 48-43 for an automatic bid to the NCAA Tournament.
videos.headline: Stanford rallies past Oregon State for Pac-12 title
